content.rendered:
The Trafalgar Tub Chair has a distinctive design with it’s winged arms and large seat.

 

The Trafalgar is manufactured in the UK and is available in 4 colours as standard. A great looking chair finished in crib 5 faux leather. Also available in COM.

Usually held in stock for delivery in 3-5 days. Other fabrics, fauxs and leathers will take 3-4 weeks.
